Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 426
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=Deviation
  - 280
By: Philalethes
---
Calcihation by means of a heterogeneous agent can only destroy the
metallic nature, in so far as it has any effect at all. Every
calcination of gold, which is not succeeded by a spontaneous
dissolution, without laying on of hands, is also fallacious.
